screen_desc: The screenshot shows a mobile app interface for entering a delivery address. At the top, there is a map with a pin that can be adjusted. Below the map, the address "17 Washington Street, Hilton SA 5033, Australia" is displayed. There are fields for "Apartment/Suite" and "Entry code." The "Drop-off Options" section allows the user to choose between "Hand it to me" and "Leave it at my door," with the latter option selected. There is a text box for additional instructions, such as ringing the bell after dropoff or leaving the package next to the porch. At the bottom, there is a red "Save Address" button.

ui_elements.text: e.g. ring the bell after dropoff leave next to the porch call upon arrival etc.Do not add order changes or requests here.
